<%- include('partials/head') %>
<h1 class="page serif">You've been invited to settle</h1>
<p class="sub">Someone wants to resolve a dispute with you on MidBid. Review the details, then accept to join — or decline.</p>
<div class="card">
  <h2><%= c.title %></h2>
  <p class="muted" style="margin:.3rem 0 1rem">Case MB-<%= c.id %> · £<%= fmt(c.amount) %> in dispute</p>
  <p>If you accept, you'll privately set the figure you can live with —
    <strong><%= c.claimant_id == null ? 'the least you will accept' : 'the most you will pay' %></strong>.
    The other side never sees your number; you only get a signal when you're close, and it settles
    in the middle if your figures cross.</p>
  <div class="btn-block">
    <form method="POST" action="/join/<%= c.invite_token %>" style="display:inline">
      <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Accept &amp; join this case</button>
    </form>
    <form method="POST" action="/decline/<%= c.invite_token %>" style="display:inline;margin-left:.5rem"
          onsubmit="return confirm('Decline this case? The other party will be told you declined.');">
      <button class="btn" type="submit">Decline</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>
<%- include('partials/foot') %>
